extends layout

block content
  section#home.home
    .container
      .row 
        .col-md-6.intro
          h2.black Hello 
          p My Name is Ian Behrmann, and I develop web applications!
          p I love developing complex back-end solutions, with the end goal of detailed data visualization.  Visualizing data in a world where it is constantly available, and constantly changing - motivates me to improve and find new ways to express myself.

          h2.black About me
          p A Colorado native, and an avid snowboarder.  I love being outdoors but am also thrilled and intrigued by the progression of video game technology.
        .col-md-6.personal
          img(src='/images/headshot.jpg')
