      .portfolio-section
        .row
          .col-md-10.col-md-offset-1
            h4.text-center.white A couple of the projects I have been working on. Galvanize capstone project coming soon...
        .row.margin-top
          .col-md-6
            figure.portfolio-img
              img.img-responsive(src="/images/colorado-disc.png")
              figcaption
                a.margin-left(href="#") Colorado-Disc Site
            h4.margin-top.text-center.white An application for Colorado Disc Golf players to help manage their progress and track scores with d3 visualizatoin.
          .col-md-6
            figure.portfolio-img
              img.img-responsive(src="/images/grafique.png")
              figcaption.hover-mask
                a.margin-left(href="https://grafique.cfapps.io/") D3 Pie Chart Generator
            h4.margin-top.text-center.white A single page Angular app that allows you to dynamicly generate pie charts and export the corresponding d3 code snippet.
